            <string>Render Buckets</string>
            <key>FooterText</key>
            <string>Each render bucket represents five visible messages. Older messages are hidden, not deleted, and remain available to Save Context. This controls DOM rendering pressure rather than the private WebKit RAM ceiling.</string>
        </dict>
